						               													<description>ENG:&amp;#10;Go back over  1000 years in time when the area of present-day Polish territory was divided between great tribes. Each of these tribes were concentrated around the centers of power - fortified castles. Lead one of the tribes, defend against enemy attacks, conquer  the vast territories and finally try to conquer rival's stronghold. Probably you will have to fight many battles in which many brave fighters will fall.&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Grody&amp;quot; (Castles) is a strategy game for 2 players. In this title you will find a nice mix of realm building controlling conquered territories to gain Victory Points and dice based combat. Each player becomes the ruler of the castle, Sielec or Szczukczyn, and seeks to gain territorial dominance or raise the opponent's castle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PL:&amp;#10;Cofnij si&amp;#196;&amp;#153; o ponad 1000 lat w czasy, gdy obszar dzisiejszej Polski podzielony by&amp;#197;&amp;#130; na terytoria wielkoplemienne. Ka&amp;#197;&amp;#188;de z tych plemion skupione by&amp;#197;&amp;#130;o wok&amp;oacute;&amp;#197;&amp;#130; o&amp;#197;&amp;#155;rodk&amp;oacute;w w&amp;#197;&amp;#130;adzy - warownych grod&amp;oacute;w. Sta&amp;#197;&amp;#132; na czele jednego z plemion, obro&amp;#197;&amp;#132; go przed zakusami wrog&amp;oacute;w, opanuj i zagospodaruj rozleg&amp;#197;&amp;#130;e terytoria, wreszcie spr&amp;oacute;buj podbi&amp;#196;&amp;#135; gr&amp;oacute;d rywala. Zapewne b&amp;#196;&amp;#153;dziesz musia&amp;#197;&amp;#130; stoczy&amp;#196;&amp;#135; wiele bitew, w kt&amp;oacute;rych polegnie niejeden dzielny woj.&amp;#10;&amp;ldquo;Grody&amp;rdquo; to strategiczna gra planszowo - karciana dla dw&amp;oacute;ch os&amp;oacute;b. Ka&amp;#197;&amp;#188;dy z graczy staje si&amp;#196;&amp;#153; w&amp;#197;&amp;#130;adc&amp;#196;&amp;#133; grodu, Sielca lub Szczukczyna, i d&amp;#196;&amp;#133;&amp;#197;&amp;#188;y do zdobycia dominacji terytorialnej lub podbicia grodu przeciwnika.&amp;#10;&am